much more in the book.

00:26:37.210 --> 00:26:39.060 align:middle line:84%
But it gives you
a flavor, a taste.

00:26:39.060 --> 00:26:40.810 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Did yours say gymnast?

00:26:40.810 --> 00:26:42.817 align:middle line:84%
>>MILLMAN: No, nothing
that's specific.

