life patterns.

00:26:45.690 --> 00:26:46.050 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Really?

00:26:46.050 --> 00:26:47.940 align:middle line:84%
>>MILLMAN: But they
approach it differently.

00:26:47.940 --> 00:26:51.270 align:middle line:84%
They each have their own
weaknesses and strengths.

00:26:51.270 --> 00:26:55.170 align:middle line:84%
I wish I had known this system
when I was a coach at Stanford.

00:26:55.170 --> 00:26:56.040 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Wow.

00:26:56.040 --> 00:26:57.930 align:middle line:84%
And also, what about
being a gymnast

00:26:57.930 --> 00:27:00.691 align:middle line:84%
