picture of what they're actually

00:27:14.250 --> 00:27:14.790 align:middle line:90%
gaining.

00:27:14.790 --> 00:27:15.330 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes.

00:27:15.330 --> 00:27:16.210 align:middle line:90%
Yes.

00:27:16.210 --> 00:27:18.130 align:middle line:84%
>>MILLMAN: Yeah, athletes
learn a lot, as you know.

00:27:18.130 --> 00:27:19.922 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: I used to be
a competitive cyclist.

00:27:19.922 --> 00:27:23.850 align:middle line:84%
