00:27:40.975 --> 00:27:41.775 align:middle line:90%
>>MILLMAN: Yes.

00:27:41.775 --> 00:27:43.230 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: --in terms
of athletics--

00:27:43.230 --> 00:27:43.680 align:middle line:90%
>>MILLMAN: Yes.

00:27:43.680 --> 00:27:45.000 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: --raising your
dopamine together.

00:27:45.000 --> 00:27:46.860 align:middle line:84%
And you're having
great conversations.

