and well-being,

00:28:29.880 --> 00:28:33.430 align:middle line:84%
now by investing four
minutes a day in yourself.

00:28:33.430 --> 00:28:34.230 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: That's it.

00:28:34.230 --> 00:28:36.220 align:middle line:90%
Four minutes a day in yourself.

00:28:36.220 --> 00:28:38.880 align:middle line:84%
Now, what do you do when you
invest four minutes a day

00:28:38.880 --> 00:28:39.940 align:middle line:90%
in yourself?

00:28:39.940 --> 00:28:40.740 align:middle line:90%
>>MILLMAN: Well--

00:28:40.740 --> 00:28:41.290 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Four minutes?

00:28:41.290 --> 00:28:42.373 align:middle line:10%
>>MILLMAN: --I recognize--

00:28:42.373 --> 00:28:44.370 align:middle line:10%
I try to be realistic
and practical,

00:28:44.370 --> 00:28:46.440 align:middle line:10%
rather than just conceptual.

00:28:46.440 --> 00:28:49.830 align:middle line:10%
And I wanted to develop
a workout that's

00:28:49.830 --> 00:28:51.450 align:middle line:10%
almost excuse proof you can do.

00:28:51.450 --> 00:28:52.408 align:middle line:90%
And this was developed.

00:28:52.408 --> 00:28:53.895 align:middle line:90%
That was 23 years ago.

00:28:53.895 --> 00:28:55.770 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: You can do a
workout in four minutes?

00:28:55.770 --> 00:28:56.770 align:middle line:90%
>>MILLMAN: Four minutes.

00:28:56.770 --> 00:28:59.490 align:middle line:84%
It's designed and complete in
less than four minutes a day.

00:28:59.490 --> 00:29:01.567 align:middle line:84%
And it gets every
part of the body.

00:29:01.567 --> 00:29:02.400 align:middle line:90%
It's deep breathing.

00:29:02.400 --> 00:29:05.890 align:middle line:84%
That's the key to it, but also
moving every part of the body.

00:29:05.890 --> 00:29:08.580 align:middle line:84%
So I've been doing this
every day for the last--

00:29:08.580 --> 00:29:11.235 align:middle line:84%
I guess about 30
years every day.

00:29:11.235 --> 00:29:12.360 align:middle line:90%
It's the core of what I do.

00:29:12.360 --> 00:29:13.818 align:middle line:84%
And I do more than
that, but that's

00:29:13.818 --> 00:29:17.022 align:middle line:84%
what I do every day on
the road anywhere I go.

00:29:17.022 --> 00:29:19.230 align:middle line:84%
And it's based on the idea
that a little of something

00:29:19.230 --> 00:29:20.790 align:middle line:90%
is better than a lot of nothing.

00:29:20.790 --> 00:29:22.245 align:middle line:84%
It's a great way
to start the day.

00:29:22.245 --> 00:29:23.370 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: I was going to say.

00:29:23.370 --> 00:29:25.787 align:middle line:84%
>>MILLMAN: I also developed a
4-Minute Meditation, which I

00:29:25.787 --> 00:29:27.970 align:middle line:90%
also teach through my website.

00:29:27.970 --> 00:29:28.770 align:middle line:90%
Yeah.

