It's not an expensive course.

00:30:36.840 --> 00:30:39.240 align:middle line:84%
So it's accessible to
anyone, pretty much.

00:30:39.240 --> 00:30:41.160 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: I mean,
when anyone asks me,

00:30:41.160 --> 00:30:43.560 align:middle line:84%
what is your secret
or your trick

00:30:43.560 --> 00:30:46.110 align:middle line:90%
to living a fulfilled life?

00:30:46.110 --> 00:30:47.680 align:middle line:90%
It's always movement.

00:30:47.680 --> 00:30:51.550 align:middle line:84%
Movement does so much for
the body, and the brain--

00:30:51.550 --> 00:30:52.350 align:middle line:90%
>>MILLMAN: Yes.

00:30:52.350 --> 00:30:54.420 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: --and possibilities.

00:30:54.420 --> 00:30:56.520 align:middle line:84%
And if you don't have
the means to move,

00:30:56.520 --> 00:31:00.150 align:middle line:84%
