00:31:00.150 --> 00:31:00.990 align:middle line:90%
from a chair--

00:31:00.990 --> 00:31:01.790 align:middle line:90%
>>MILLMAN: Sure.

00:31:01.790 --> 00:31:06.480 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: --as long as you
get the blood circulating.

00:31:06.480 --> 00:31:08.450 align:middle line:90%
It's a huge piece.

00:31:08.450 --> 00:31:10.200 align:middle line:84%
>>MILLMAN: It's a
little bit of something,

00:31:10.200 --> 00:31:12.720 align:middle line:84%
and that's important
for anybody.

00:31:12.720 --> 00:31:16.347 align:middle line:84%
I recommend that people
dream big, but start small

00:31:16.347 --> 00:31:17.430 align:middle line:90%
and then connect the dots.

00:31:17.430 --> 00:31:19.150 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: And start somewhere.

