>>MILLMAN: Sure.

00:31:23.240 --> 00:31:23.810 align:middle line:90%
Sure.

00:31:23.810 --> 00:31:24.780 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: But you've got
to start somewhere.

00:31:24.780 --> 00:31:25.470 align:middle line:90%
>>MILLMAN: Starting small.

